		image_class: 'image-horizontal',
		parragraphs: ['One of our crew remarks how odd it is that these bones still lie here strewn about without being catalogued and open for anyone to loot. Lucio helps us understand the urgency of revealing the wonder at Monte Sierpe\'s true nature: "Peru is full of ancient burial and ritual sites - especially near the coast where the climate is particularly dry and preserves them\u201D.']
